Male terminalia (Fig. 12
A-D
): epandrium with ca. 16 setae near posterior and ventral margins per side. Surstylus with 6-7 peg-like prensisetae. Hypandrium with a pair of paramedian setae, lacking pubescence. Paramere with six sensilla subbasally and pubescence distally. Aedeagus lacking pubescence.
